{"tid":483701,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(特發冇圖) 大概只有他才能拯救香港樂壇","createTime":"2017-11-29T11:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T14:16:48.000Z","uid":64829,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fdc65ae7d0db2814744ca74d80f4c5e211787931","tid":483701,"uid":64829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T11:16:59.000Z","msg":"「祝&hellip;祝&hellip;&hellip;祝福聲想你都聽到&hellip;」<br />\n「誰人又相 &uarr; 信&hellip; 一世一生這膚淺對白&hellip; 來吧送給～你&hellip;」<br />\n「能共你 hole &uarr; hole &uarr; 地相處&hellip;」<br />\n曾經，黃宗澤嘅歌曲，一首接一首咁打入樂迷心房。無論係【最後祝福】抑或【K歌之王】，澤囝嘅實力都係無容置疑，理應可以喺樂壇闖出一片天。<br />\n可惜，主流頒獎禮一直忽視其實力，令大批樂迷為佢大感不值之餘，澤囝本人亦唱到無癮，於數年前封咪，關上金嗓子，黯然離開樂壇。<br />\n黃宗澤嘅離開，為處於彌留狀態嘅香港樂壇再注入四毫升毒藥，引致近年樂壇暗淡失色，死多兩錢重。但，捱過黑暗日子就會迎來光明，2018 年嘅樂壇，終於看見來自拯救者嘅曙光。<br />\n漫長等待 is finally over，黃宗澤終於再次進入久違嘅錄音室灌錄新歌了！我好興奮呀！「你們猜猜，究竟我們在幹什麼？」鬼馬嘅澤囝留言，但與監製的合照已出賣咗佢，錄緊新歌囉！澤囝高舉反 V 手勢，心情不俗，看來新歌質素理想。據悉，消息感動全港歌迷，紛紛闖入網絡平台重溫澤囝舊作，作好準備迎來其新作。<br />\n香港樂壇欠黃宗澤實在太多，但澤神仍然不離不棄。我們一同期待澤囝今次復出，拯救糜爛嘅樂壇。<br />\n#2018年我最喜愛的男歌手 <br />\n//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////<br />\n延伸閱讀－澤囝經典作品重溫：<br />\n【K歌之王】秒殺嘍囉陳奕迅<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kingjerentertainment/videos/1080500132021850/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkingjerentertainment%2Fvideos%2F1080500132021850%2F&d=ER1fNaPKqYanJ41WBwuhiwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=3bc8e34b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kingjerentertainment/videos/1080500132021850/</a><br />\n【最後祝福】唱出退出樂壇心情<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kingjerentertainment/videos/1082358428502687/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkingjerentertainment%2Fvideos%2F1082358428502687%2F&d=ER1fNaPKqYanJ41WBwuhiwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=614ea751\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kingjerentertainment/videos/1082358428502687/</a><br />\n【This on9 Jai】黃宗澤表演拿手快歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kingjerentertainment/videos/1084256971646166/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkingjerentertainment%2Fvideos%2F1084256971646166%2F&d=ER1fNaPKqYanJ41WBwuhiwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=70af36b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kingjerentertainment/videos/1084256971646166/</a><br />\n【最後祝福】退出樂壇後鮮有的公開表演<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kingjerentertainment/videos/1092310327507497/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkingjerentertainment%2Fvideos%2F1092310327507497%2F&d=ER1fNaPKqYanJ41WBwuhiwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=84d86991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kingjerentertainment/videos/1092310327507497/</a><br />\n【餓狼傳說】澤囝置身東莞舞池跳唱張學友神曲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kingjerentertainment/videos/1412018885536638/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkingjerentertainment%2Fvideos%2F1412018885536638%2F&d=ER1fNaPKqYanJ41WBwuhiwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=bbb340a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kingjerentertainment/videos/1412018885536638/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/191536_ea1f0a7473c709fecdca04bac7093350.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F191536_ea1f0a7473c709fecdca04bac7093350.png&h=c62c4e1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1c944fddf2cae6742b517bee9e0f4d8e332a78a","tid":483701,"uid":64829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T11:17:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/2018%E5%B9%B4%E6%88%91%E6%9C%80%E5%96%9C%E6%84%9B%E7%9A%84%E7%94%B7%E6%AD%8C%E6%89%8B?source=feed_text&amp;story_id=1742392405832616\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhashtag%2F2018%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%2596%259C%25E6%2584%259B%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2594%25B7%25E6%25A